er-file.png","alt":"Profile Photo"}}]},{"type":"flex-column","classes":["gjs-plg-flex-column"],"attributes":{"data-type-role":"flex-column","id":"ibannercol2"},"components":[{"tagName":"h2","type":"heading","attributes":{"id":"ibannername"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Hi, I’m Paige."}]},{"tagName":"h3","type":"heading","attributes":{"id":"ibannerrole"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Flutist, teacher, illustrator"}]},{"tagName":"p","type":"text","attributes":{"id":"ibannertext"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Building exceptional digital experiences through innovative design and cutting-edge development. Specializing in creating user-centered solutions that drive results and exceed expectations."}]},{"type":"flex-row","classes":["gjs-plg-flex-row"],"attributes":{"data-type-role":"flex-row","id":"ibannerbtn"},"components":[{"type":"linkBox","classes":["gjs-link-box"],"attributes":{"href":"#about","id":"ibtn1"},"components":[{"tagName":"span","type":"text","attributes":{"id":"ibtn1text"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Read More"}]}]}],"snap":"","snap-divisions":12}]}],"snap":"","snap-divisions":12}]}],"custom-name":"Home Landing"},{"type":"section","classes":["gjs-section"],"attributes":{"id":"about"},"components":[{"type":"container","classes":["gjs-container"],"attributes":{"id":"iabtcnt"},"components":[{"type":"flex-column","classes":["gjs-plg-flex-column"],"attributes":{"data-type-role":"flex-column","id":"iabtheader"},"components":[{"tagName":"h2","type":"heading","attributes":{"id":"iabttitle"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"About Me"}]}]},{"type":"flex-row","classes":["gjs-plg-flex-row"],"attributes":{"data-type-role":"flex-row","id":"iabtrow"},"components":[{"type":"flex-column","classes":["gjs-plg-flex-column"],"attributes":{"data-type-role":"flex-column","id":"iabtcol1"},"components":[{"tagName":"p","type":"text","attributes":{"id":"iabtdesc"},"components":[{"tagName":"meta","void":true,"attributes":{"http-equiv":"Content-Type","content":"text/html; charset=utf-8"}},{"tagName":"meta","void":true,"attributes":{"name":"ProgId","content":"Word.Document"}},{"tagName":"meta","void":true,"attributes":{"name":"Generator","content":"Microsoft Word 15"}},{"tagName":"meta","void":true,"attributes":{"name":"Originator","content":"Microsoft Word 15"}},{"tagName":"link","void":true,"attributes":{"rel":"File-List","href":"file:///C:/Users/Paige/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_filelist.xml"}},{"tagName":"link","void":true,"attributes":{"rel":"themeData","href":"file:///C:/Users/Paige/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_themedata.thmx"}},{"tagName":"link","void":true,"attributes":{"rel":"colorSchemeMapping","href":"file:///C:/Users/Paige/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_colorschememapping.xml"}},{"tagName":"p","type":"text","classes":["MsoNormal"],"attributes":{"id":"iy6of"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Paige Douglas is an active chamber and solo musician in Tallahassee, Florida. She is currently a flute performance major at Florida State University (FSU), class of 2026. She frequently performs with FSU’s graduate-level bands and orchestras, and she is currently co-principal of the University Symphony Orchestra. She participated in the Florida Flute Association 2023 and 2024 conferences with the FSU Flute Ensemble."}]},{"components":[{"tagName":"br","void":true}]},{"tagName":"p","type":"text","classes":["MsoNormal"],"attributes":{"id":"iqini"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Douglas studies with Dr. Karen Large and Dr. Mary Matthews at FSU. In her hometown of Maryville, Tennessee, she studied with Knoxville Symphony Orchestra member Zach Millwood and previous Maryville College professor of flute Nathalie Simper. "}]},{"components":[{"tagName":"br","void":true}]},{"tagName":"p","type":"text","classes":["MsoNormal"],"attributes":{"id":"ifpoo"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Alongside her flute studies, Douglas is also an active painter and animator. This February, her work “Glowing” was featured in Blackberry Mountain’s"},{"tagName":"em","type":"text","components":[{"type":"textnode","content":" Perennial Ties"}]},{"type":"textnode","content":" group exhibition. She also collaborated with the Khemia Ensemble to create a series of animations for their show"},{"tagName":"em","type":"text","components":[{"type":"textnode","content":" all the lives we lived"}]},{"type":"textnode","content":". "}]}]},{"type":"linkBox","classes":["gjs-link-box"],"attributes":{"href":"https://fsu-my.sharepoint.com/:b:/g/personal/pmd22_fsu_edu/IQBMHGaPRgUDSIAuJ-bLceKoAV4hFpOnYY4DIXjGXnsTwcY?e=f7PCBP","id":"ibtn1-2","download":"Paige-Douglas-CV.pdf","aria-label":"Download my CV as PDF"},"components":[{"tagName":"span","type":"text","attributes":{"id":"ibtn1text-2"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Download My CV"}]}],"hrefType":"url"}]},{"type":"flex-column","classes":["gjs-plg-flex-column"],"attributes":{"data-type-role":"flex-column","id":"iabtcol2"},"components":[{"type":"image","resizable":{"ratioDefault":1},"attributes":{"id":"iabtimg","src":"https://cdn.grapesjs.com/workspaces/cmms2nlou1a6n3ccnpj2h7yx5/assets/863d12b8-e005-449c-bc05-0a767fcab848__headshot-smaller-file-cropped.png","alt":"About Image"}}]}],"snap":"","snap-divisions":12}]}],"custom-name":"About"},{"type":"section","classes":["gjs-section"],"attributes":{"id":"services"},"components":[{"type":"container","classes":["gjs-container"],"attributes":{"id":"isrvcnt"},"components":[{"type":"flex-column","classes":["gjs-plg-flex-column"],"attributes":{"data-type-role":"flex-column","id":"isrvheader"},"components":[{"tagName":"h2","type":"heading","attributes":{"id":"isrvtitle"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"My Services"}]},{"tagName":"p","type":"text","attributes":{"id":"isrvsubtitle"},"components":[{"type":"textnode","content":"Offering a comprehensive range of creative and technical services to help bring your 